Describe Options task
    Before each
        call PrepareForTest()
    End

    It Options task
        CreateTasksfile
        @task.options
        def thing(ctx):
            foo = 'FOO'
            bar = 'BAR'
            baz = 'BAZ'

        @task(thing)
        def check(ctx, value):
            assert ctx.dep.thing == value
.
        OP thing foo
        OP check FOO

        OP thing bar
        OP check BAR

        OP thing baz
        OP check BAZ
    End
End
